{
  "info": {
    "name": "TaskTracker - Iteration 0",
    "description": "Health-check and API basic structure validation tests for TaskTracker Iteration 0 (Foundation)\n\nIteráció 0 tesztek:\n- API response shape validálása (success + data)\n- Health-check endpoint tesztelése\n- HTTP status kódok ellenőrzése\n- Response headers validálása",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json",
    "version": "1.0.0"
  },
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "Health Check",
      "event": [
        {
          "listen": "test",
          "script": {
            "exec": [
              "// Status code validation",
              "pm.test('Status code is 200', function () {",
              "  pm.response.to.have.status(200);",
              "});",
              "",
              "// Response time validation",
              "pm.test('Response time is less than 1000ms', function () {",
              "  pm.expect(pm.response.responseTime).to.be.below(1000);",
              "});",
              "",
              "// Parse response body",
              "const responseJson = pm.response.json();",
              "",
              "// Validate response structure has 'success' property",
              "pm.test('Response has success property', function () {",
              "  pm.expect(responseJson).to.have.property('success');",
              "});",
              "",
              "// Validate success property is boolean",
              "pm.test('Success property is a boolean', function () {",
              "  pm.expect(responseJson.success).to.be.a('boolean');",
              "});",
              "",
              "// Validate response has 'data' property",
              "pm.test('Response has data property', function () {",
              "  pm.expect(responseJson).to.have.property('data');",
              "});",
              "",
              "// Validate data is an object",
              "pm.test('Data property is an object', function () {",
              "  pm.expect(responseJson.data).to.be.an('object');",
              "});",
              "",
              "// Validate the success value is true for health-check",
              "pm.test('Health-check returns success: true', function () {",
              "  pm.expect(responseJson.success).to.equal(true);",
              "});",
              "",
              "// Validate response headers",
              "pm.test('Content-Type is application/json', function () {",
              "  pm.expect(pm.response.headers.get('Content-Type')).to.include('application/json');",
              "});",
              "",
              "// Validate response size is reasonable",
              "pm.test('Response size is less than 1KB', function () {",
              "  pm.expect(pm.response.text().length).to.be.below(1024);",
              "});"
            ],
            "type": "text/javascript"
          }
        }
      ],
      "request": {
        "method": "GET",
        "header": [
          {
            "key": "Accept",
            "value": "application/json",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ],
        "url": {
          "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/",
          "host": [
            "{{baseUrl}}"
          ],
          "path": [
            ""
          ]
        },
        "description": "Health-check endpoint that returns basic API structure validation.\n\nExpected response format:\n```json\n{\n  \"success\": true,\n  \"data\": {}\n}\n```\n\nEz a végpont igazolja, hogy az alkalmazás elérhető és az API response shape helyesen van konfigurálva."
      },
      "response": [
        {
          "name": "Success - Health Check OK",
          "originalRequest": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Accept",
                "value": "application/json",
                "type": "text"
              }
            ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/",
              "host": [
                "{{baseUrl}}"
              ],
              "path": [
                ""
              ]
            }
          },
          "status": "OK",
          "code": 200,
          "header": [
            {
              "key": "Content-Type",
              "value": "application/json; charset=utf-8"
            },
            {
              "key": "Content-Length",
              "value": "21"
            }
          ],
          "body": "{\"success\":true,\"data\":{}}"
        }
      ]
    }
  ],
  "variable": [
    {
      "key": "baseUrl",
      "value": "{{baseUrl}}",
      "type": "string"
    }
  ]
}
